    ),

    len,
    pos;

pos = new Point(

  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }

    len,
    pos;

pos = new Point(

  len * Math.cos(radians(this.direction())));
pos = pos.add(new Point(this.xPosition(), this.yPosition()));
this.gotoXY(pos.x, pos.y, false);
this.changed();
if (isWarped) {this.startWarp(); }
